These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-4-1::.
City: london, san-francisco
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, tiparillo
House: tower, cape-cod
2 different games are played: go, mah-jongg
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, bus
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, october
1. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person traveling to london is the tiparillo-smoker##1
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an even position##4
5. the person playing mah-jongg is the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |
| City      | london   | san-francisco        |
| Cigar          | tiparillo    | ritmeester     |
| House         | cape-cod | tower   |
| Game           | go  | mah-jongg |
| Transport   | motorbike   | bus       |
| Birthday           | october   | april      |

