.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: lavender, fuchsia
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: bellflower, sunflower
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: spy, documentary
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, september
City: london, prague
House: tower, futuristic
1. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
2. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
3. the person who likes lavender is in an odd position##4
4. the person who growssunflower is the person watching documentary movies##1
5. the futuristic house is on the right of the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Color      | lavender       | fuchsia      |
| Flower          | bellflower   | sunflower |
| Movie-Genre         | spy | documentary  |
| Birthday   | september        | august     |
| City   | london       | prague   |
| House           | tower        | futuristic |

